def extract_info(input_str):
    info = {}
    # Extract DateOfBirth
    date_of_birth = re.search(r'Dob is (\d{2}-\d{2}-\d{4})', input_str)
    if date_of_birth:
        info['DateOfBirth'] = date_of_birth.group(1)
    else:
        info['DateOfBirth'] = 'empty'

    # Extract PhoneNumber
    phone_number = re.search(r'Phone no : (\d+)', input_str)
    if phone_number:
        info['PhoneNumber'] = phone_number.group(1)
    else:
        info['PhoneNumber'] = 'empty'

    # Extract Email
    email = re.search(r'(\w+@\w+\.\w+)', input_str)
    if email:
        info['Email'] = email.group(0)
    else:
        info['Email'] = 'empty'

    # Extract FirstName and LastName

    if name:
        info['FirstName'] = name.group(0)

    else:

        info['LastName'] = 'empty'

import re

def extract_info(user_input):
    info = {
        'FirstName': '',
        'LastName': '',
        'DateOfBirth': '',
        'Email': '',
        'PhoneNumber': '',
        'PreferredDateOrTime': ''
    }

    # Extract PreferredDateOrTime
    info['PreferredDateOrTime'] = user_input

    # Extract Email
    email_match = re.search(r'\b[A-Za-z0-9._%+-]+@[A-Za-z0-9.-]+\.[A-Z|a-z]{2,}\b', user_input)
    if email_match:
        info['Email'] = email_match.group()

    # Extract PhoneNumber
    phone_match = re.search(r'\d{3}[-\s]?\d{3}[-\s]?\d{4}', user_input)
    if phone_match:
        info['PhoneNumber'] = phone_match.group()

    # Extract FirstName and LastName
    words = user_input.split()

         import re

def extract_info(user_input):
    # Extract FirstName
    FirstName = re.search(r'(?<=is )\w+', user_input).group()
    
    # Extract LastName
    LastName = re.search(r'(?<=James, )\w+', user_input).group()
    
    # Extract DateOfBirth
    DateOfBirth = re.search(r'Dob is (\d{1,2}-\d{1,2}-\d{4})', user_input).group(1)
    
    # Extract Email
    Email = re.search(r'\b\w+@\w+\.\w+\b', user_input).group()
    
    # Extract PhoneNumber
    PhoneNumber = re.search(r'Phone no : (\d+)', user_input).group(1)
    
    # Extract PreferredDateOrTime
    PreferredDateOrTime = re.search(r'prefered date and time is : (.*?) at', user_input, re.DOTALL).group(1)
    
    return {
        '0': {'FirstName': FirstName, 'LastName': LastName, 'DateOfBirth': DateOfBirth, 'Email': Email, 'PhoneNumber': PhoneNumber, 'PreferredDateOrTime': PreferredDateOrTime}
    }

def extract_info(user_input):
    # Initialize an empty dictionary to store the extracted information
    extracted_info = {
        'FirstName': '',
        'LastName': '',
        'DateOfBirth': '',
        'Email': '',
        'PhoneNumber': '',
        'PreferredDateOrTime': ''
    }

    # Extract DateOfBirth
    dob_match = re.search(r'Dob is (\d{2}-\d{2}-\d{4})', user_input)
    if dob_match:
        extracted_info['DateOfBirth'] = dob_match.group(1)

    # Extract Email
    email_match = re.search(r'(\S+@\S+)', user_input)
    if email_match:
        extracted_info['Email'] = email_match.group(1)

    # Extract PhoneNumber
    phone_match = re.search(r'Phone no : (\d+)', user_input)
    if phone_match:
        extracted_info['PhoneNumber'] = phone_match.group(1)

    # Extract FirstName and LastName
    name_match = re.search(r'(\w+)\s(\w+)', user_input)
    if name_match:
        extracted_info['FirstName'] = name_match.group(1)
        extracted_info['LastName'] = name_match.group(2)
